name: Static Charge
description:
Sometimes there is an imbalance or uncertainty in the air - maybe it’s something electrical, or a special connection, between you and a special person, an interesting place, or that unique object. Sometimes that feeling and that charge remains with you indefinitely - a static hum that vibrates across time and space, a memory or a feeling, a power that you can recall at will.
